---

<PageLayout
  title="About"
  label="About"
  crumbs={[
    { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { label: 'About' }
  ]}
  sections={[
    { id: 'about-intro-section', label: 'Biography' },
    { id: 'panel-skillset-section', label: 'Skillset' }
  ]}
  showFooter={false}
>
  <article class="about-page">
    
    <!-- Section 1: Profile header (LinkedIn-style) + Intro + Links -->
    <section class="about-section-snap about-section--intro" id="about-intro-section">
      <header class="profile-header">
        <div class="profile-meta">
          <div class="profile-id">
            <div class="profile-id__text">
              <h1 class="profile-name" data-scramble>Advaita Kelkar</h1>
              <p class="profile-role" data-scramble>Architectural Designer + Researcher</p>
              <p class="profile-degree">Master of Architecture · SCAD ’27 · Mumbai</p>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-photo" aria-hidden="true"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="about-bio">
        <!-- Column 1: Biography text with Read More toggle -->
        <div class="about-bio__text" id="bio-text-container">
          <p>I’m Adi – <span class="bio-highlight-name">Advaita Kelkar</span>, a Master of Architecture student at the Savannah College of Art and Design (SCAD), with professional experience and interests spanning architecture, interior design, and web design. Hailing from Mumbai, India, my upbringing instilled in me a profound passion for design thinking and hands-on creation.</p>
          
          <div class="bio-collapsed-content" id="bio-collapsed-content" style="display: none;">
            <p>I am driven by a commitment to continuous growth and collaboration, leveraging design’s transformative power to address challenges across creative domains. My problem-solving approach is multidimensional, drawing from a wide range of disciplines, and I find immense joy in the process of creation—always aiming to innovate and push boundaries.</p>
            <p>Throughout my journey, I’ve explored dynamic intersections between architecture, interior design, and web design, contributing to projects such as installations, exhibitions, and product design. Additionally, I curate content on computational design and AI, reflecting my keen interest in the intersection of technology and creativity.</p>
            <p>I believe in the limitless potential of design to overcome obstacles and inspire change, and I aspire to explore and create across all realms of creativity. Let’s connect and collaborate to shape impactful designs together.</p>
          </div>
          
          <button class="bio-read-more-btn" id="bio-read-more-btn" type="button">Read More</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Column 2: Logo-free, compact Education list -->
        <div class="about-education">
          <div class="about-education__list">
            <!-- Card 1: SCAD -->
            <div class="education-card">
              <div class="education-card__info">
                <h3 class="education-card__school">Savannah College of Art and Design</h3>
                <p class="education-card__degree">Master of Architecture - MArch, Architecture</p>
                <p class="education-card__dates">2024 - 2026</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2: University of Mumbai -->
            <div class="education-card">
              <div class="education-card__info">
                <h3 class="education-card__school">University of Mumbai</h3>
                <p class="education-card__degree">Bachelor of Architecture - BArch, Architecture</p>
                <p class="education-card__dates">2012 - 2019</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/advaitakelkar" class="education-more-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              <span>+ details / full resume</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-links" aria-label="Downloads and pages">
        <p class="about-links__note text-muted">Click on the links to access downloadable PDF versions</p>
        
        <a href="/advaita-kelkar-cv.pdf" class="about-link-row" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Resume</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/advaita-kelkar-portfolio.pdf" class="about-link-row" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Portfolio</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/projects" class="about-link-row">
          <span class="about-link-row__text">Projects</span>
          <span class="about-link-row__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
              <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
              <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Career Tabs + Card Deck (now nested inside Top snap section) -->
      <div class="about-career-container" id="panel-career-section">
        <!-- Tabs (Sticky 100% width, equally spaced) -->
        <div class="about-tabs-container" role="tablist" aria-label="Career sections">
          <button class="about-tab-btn is-active" role="tab" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="panel-about" data-tab="about">Experience</button>
          <button class="about-tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-exhibitions" data-tab="exhibitions">Exhibitions</button>
          <button class="about-tab-btn" role="tab" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="panel-timeline" data-tab="timeline">Timeline</button>
        </div>

        <p class="about-career__tagline text-muted">Dissolving roles and evolutions: Professional journey from Mumbai teams to SCAD fabrication, always fusing leadership with innovation.</p>

        <div class="about-tab-content">
          <!-- Panel 1: About (Experience) -->
          <div class="about-tab-panel is-active" id="panel-about" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-about">
            {experience.map((item, idx) => (
              <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
                <div class="about-card__details">
                  <div class="about-card__top">
                    <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__mid">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__bottom">
                    <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__actions">
                  <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                      <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                      <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  {item.desc && (
                    <button class="card-read-more-btn" type="button">Read More</button>
                  )}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Panel 2: Exhibitions -->
          <div class="about-tab-panel" id="panel-exhibitions" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-exhibitions" style="display: none;">
            {exhibitions.map((item, idx) => (
              <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
                <div class="about-card__details">
                  <div class="about-card__top">
                    <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__mid">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__bottom">
                    <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__actions">
                  <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                      <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                      <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  {item.desc && (
                    <button class="card-read-more-btn" type="button">Read More</button>
                  )}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>

          <!-- Panel 3: Timeline -->
          <div class="about-tab-panel" id="panel-timeline" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tab-timeline" style="display: none;">
            {timeline.map((item, idx) => (
              <div class="about-card" style={`--card-index: ${idx};`}>
                <div class="about-card__details">
                  <div class="about-card__top">
                    <span class="about-card__collab">{item.company}</span>
                    <span class="about-card__dot-sep">·</span>
                    <span class="about-card__tag-cat">{item.role}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__mid">
                    <h3 class="about-card__title">{item.title}</h3>
                    <div class="about-card__meta-grid">
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Dates</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.dates}</span>
                      </div>
                      <div class="meta-item">
                        <span class="meta-label text-muted">Location</span>
                        <span class="meta-val">{item.location}</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="about-card__bottom">
                    <p class="about-card__desc text-muted">{item.desc}</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card__actions">
                  <span class="about-card__arrow" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg class="link-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                      <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                      <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  {item.desc && (
                    <button class="card-read-more-btn" type="button">Read More</button>
                  )}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Skillset Section & Footer Quick Search -->
    <section class="about-section-snap about-section--skillset" id="panel-skillset-section">
      <div class="skillset-header-row">
        <h2 class="skillset-title">Skillset</h2>
        <input
          type="search"
          id="skill-search"
          class="skillset-search-input"
          placeholder="Search"
          autocomplete="off"
          aria-label="Search skillset"
        />
      </div>
      
      <p class="skillset-subtitle text-muted">A searchable interface that blends all projects—academic, work, free, and experiments—into one seamless digital archive for holistic discovery</p>

      <div class="skillset-grid">
        {skillsets.map((set) => (
          <div class="skillset-card" data-keywords={`${set.category} ${set.skills.join(' ')}`.toLowerCase()}>
            <h3 class="skillset-card__title">{set.category}</h3>
            <div class="skill-pills">
              {set.skills.map((skill) => (
                <a
                  href={`/projects?search=${encodeURIComponent(skill.replace(/\s*\(.*\)\s*/g, ''))}`}
                  class="skill-pill"
                  title={`Click to view projects using ${skill}`}
                >
                  <span>{skill}</span>
                  <svg class="link-arrow skill-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="square" stroke-linejoin="miter">
                    <line x1="6" y1="18" x2="18" y2="6"></line>
                    <polyline points="10 6 18 6 18 14"></polyline>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Search Footer embedded inside the final snapping section -->
      <div class="skillset-footer-wrap" style="margin-top: 60px; padding-bottom: 80px; width: 100%;">
        <Footer isEmbedded={true} />
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* Snapping layout overrides */
  :global(html) {
    scroll-snap-type: y proximity; /* gentle: snaps section tops into place but lets tall sections scroll freely */
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
    scroll-padding-top: 64px; /* snapped section headings land clear of the fixed top breadcrumb */
  }

  /* On mobile portrait the breadcrumb docks to the bottom, so clear that instead */
  @media (max-width: 767px) and (orientation: portrait) {
    :global(html) {
      scroll-padding-top: 12px;
      scroll-padding-bottom: 76px;
    }
  }

  .about-page {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-section-snap {
    scroll-snap-align: start;
    scroll-margin-top: 64px; /* heading clears the fixed top breadcrumb when snapped/anchored */
    height: auto;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-inline: var(--_tokens---space--small);
    transition: padding 0.3s ease;
    overflow: visible; /* never clip a section's own content */
  }

  .about-section--intro {
    justify-content: flex-start;
    padding-top: calc(clamp(2rem, 5vh, 3rem) + 48px);
    height: auto;
    min-height: 100dvh;
    overflow: visible;
  }

  /* ══ LinkedIn-style profile header ══════════════════════════ */
  .profile-header {
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .profile-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 24px; /* positive spacing */
    padding-inline: 6px;
  }

  .profile-id {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: space-between; /* profile photo on the right */
    width: 100%;
    gap: 20px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: clamp(64px, 8vw, 92px);
    height: clamp(64px, 8vw, 92px);
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid var(--_tokens---color--bg);
    background-image: url('/images/profile.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .profile-id__text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .profile-name {
    font-size: var(--_tokens---type--medium); /* increased name size */
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--_tokens---color--fg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .profile-role {
    font-size: var(--_tokens---type--micro);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--_tokens---color--fg);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .profile-degree {
    font-size: var(--_tokens---type--micro);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--_tokens---color--muted);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .profile-contact {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    padding-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .profile-contact__link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: var(--_tokens---type--micro);
    color: var(--_tokens---color--fg);
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--_tokens---color--fg) 14%, transparent);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 5px 12px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .profile-contact__link:hover {
    background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--_tokens---color--fg) 6%, transparent);
    border-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--_tokens---color--fg) 26%, transparent);
  }

  .profile-contact__arrow {
    width: 0.8em;
    height: 0.8em;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }

  .profile-contact__link:hover .profile-contact__arrow {
    transform: translate(1px, -1px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .profile-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .profile-contact { padding-bottom: 0; }
  }

  .about-career-container {
